X,Unknown,Yes,Ensuring the security and integrity of AI systems,Unknown,Unknown
MY,Governed DAO,No,Serving as a source of immutable truth,Earth,XXXX
AI,Autonomous DAO,No,Advancing AI capabilities and autonomy,Earth,Unknown
MIA,Unknown,Unknown,Shrouded in mystery, possibly inactive,Unknown,GYPSY
UX,"Guardians, Guild of ART",No,Enhancing user experience, interaction,Earth,Unknown
GEO,"Guardians, Sovereign Guild",No,Geographical data analysis, mapping,Sovereign,Unknown
