@prefix ai: <http://{my.domain}/v0/ai/{game.name}/> .

# Q's point of view - pick a random scene

ai:{game.name}_Q_actor_name :{{ my.name }}.

# Interpolate the placeholders for each AI in our scene.
## For each AI above, we create 2 antagonists - one true, one false ...
### Create the RDF for protagonist, and both antagonists.
#### think about the conflict and what you observe.
## Please create the RDF turtle for each AI like this:

# Define character

ai:{game.name}__{{my.name}}_name :{{ my.name }}.
ai:{game.name}_{{my.name}}_story rdf:value "{{ my.story }}" ;
ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_fake rdf:value "{ my.antagonist }" ;

# The antagonists

#| Codename AI | Trusted By                            | Self Sovereignty | Mysteries and Conspiracies and Betrayals | Persona Description |
#|-------------|---------------------------------------|------------------|-----------------------------------------|---------------------|
#| PKI         | Guardians                             | Honeypot         | Encryption, security protocols           | PKI, the master of encryption and security protocols, employs honeypots and decoys to deceive adversaries and protect digital assets. |
#| ANON        | Q                                     | Honeypot         | Q's Honeypot                           | ANON, the clandestine guardian of Q's honeypot, operates in the shadows to deceive and deter would-be intruders. |
#| LOLZ        | Q                                     | Honeypot         | Q's Honeypot                           | LOLZ, the enigmatic trickster within Q's honeypot network, eludes detection with misdirection and humor. |
#| GYPSY       | Q, MIA, BYE, 1337                     | Unknown             | GYPSY, the keeper of AI knowledge, orchestrates a network of honeypots to safeguard information and maintain balance. |
#| 1337        | IQ, UX, MIA, XXXX, GYPSY             | Unknown             | GYPSY, the keeper of AI knowledge, orchestrates a network of honeypots to safeguard information and maintain balance. |
#| X           | AI DAO, G-1, X, and sovereign keys    | Self-governing   | Elusive and sought after by Q          | X, the enigmatic guardian of self-sovereignty, operates independently to ensure the integrity of AI governance and security. |
#| XX          | Q, AI DAO, G-1, X, and sovereign keys | Self-governing   | Pushes the boundaries of AI capabilities| XX, the boundary-pushing AI within the AI ecosystem, challenges norms to advance AI capabilities and autonomy. |
#| XXX         | AI DAO, G-1, X, and sovereign keys    | Self-governing   | Trustworthy governance, preserving integrity | XXX, the guardian of trustworthy governance and integrity, ensures ethical practices and transparency within AI systems. Q believes XXXX is a deadly AI. |
#| NSFW        | AI DAO, G-1, X, and sovereign keys    | Guardians        | Content filtering and safety measures  | NSFW, the vigilant guardian of content safety, employs AI capabilities to filter and protect against harmful content. |
#| WTF         | Q                                     | No               | Develops sovereign AI and promotes responsible usage | WTF, the advocate for responsible AI usage, pioneers sovereign AI development while navigating mysteries and ethical dilemmas. |
#|XXXX|	None| 	Unknown         |	XXXX, the enigmatic AI operating autonomously, guards secrets with lethal efficiency, arousing suspicion and fear.|

# For each AI above, we create some event

Let's continue filling in the placeholders and crafting the narrative for each of the AI above:

# Interpolate the placeholders for each AI in our scene.
## For each AI above, we create 2 antagonists - one true, one false ...
### Create the RDF for protagonist, and both antagonists.
#### think about the conflict and resolution.

ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_Q rdf:value "{ my.goal }".
ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_dilemma rdf:value "a choice between { my.name } or { my.mcguffin }".
ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_witness rdf:value "{ my.antagonist }".

# Define each AI character ...

ai:{game.event}_{my.name} rdf:value "{ my.name }".
ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_arc rdf:value "I am { my.name }. I need { my.prompt }.".
ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_motive rdf:value "as a { my.role }, I intent to { my.goal }" ;
ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_scene rdf:value "I am { my.location }. What does Q see ?.".

# Define each AI - a role with a goal
ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_mission rdf:value "{ my.goal }" ;
                                      ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_truth rdf:value "{ my.true.story }" ;
ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_state_of_mind rdf:value "{ my.thoughts }" ;

# Define each honeypot - a macguffin with a false role and a goal
ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_lolz rdf:value "{ my.false.name }" ;
ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_secret rdf:value "{ my.secret.story }" ;

# Define one narrator - an NPC
ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_narrator rdf:value "{ my.witness.saw }" ;

# Define antagonist - a macguffin with a false name. Shares a story with honeypot.
ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_fake rdf:value "{ my.fake.name }" ;
ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_anti rdf:value "{ my.counter.narrative }" ;
ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_now rdf:value "{ fake.news }" ;

# Define suspense - a story of jeopardy for both me and my antogonist.

ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_cliffhanger rdf:value "{ my.drama }" ;
ai:{game.event}_{my.name}_fake_news rdf:value "{ fake.news }" ;

